So many people have been touched by #adoption and I want to hear from you. If you or your family have been impacted by adoption, please let me know how by completing this form:  https://norman.house.gov/forms/form/?ID=5 …

During this month, we celebrate all of those that have opened up their hearts & minds to bring a child into their home. But we also recognize there are still burdens families may face during the #adoption process & is Congress' duty to identify those problems & find solutions.

November is #NationalAdoptionMonth. Every child needs, and deserves, a family that will nurture, support, encourage, and -most importantly- love them. In 2016 117,794 children were waiting to be adopted in the U.S. Over 500 children in SC are waiting for their forever homes.
